
Podcast via https://anchor.fm/intellectualexplorersclub/episodes/Frans-de-Waal---Alpha-Males--Empathy--and-Anthropodenialism-e3bp35

Focuses on the role of alpha males in primate groups. The alpha male is a coalition builder,  must be able to keep the peace, and maintain the trust of his supporters, why also recompensing them. Conversation conducted by Peter Limberg of the Intellectual Explorers Club.

